author: USA TODAY, Ian Richardson, USA TODAY
title: Fact check: Could your December cough actually have been coronavirus? Experts say more research is needed
description: A handful of widely circulated Facebook posts have asserted that people in the United States contracted the coronavirus as early as last fall.
content:
The claim: People who suffered from a round of illness in November and December likely had the coronavirus
